midt stage manager jenny schnabl assitant stage manager edwin johnson setprop design kate foster light design toby schneider soundposterprogram design ruth steinhardt costume design and edgardo costasbracero hairmakeup design orchestral pit matthew wollin flute avalon gulley clarinet stephen webste bass clarinet katie quinn horn amanda korman trumpet eugenie du violin sarah macwright violin michele chinitz viola sarah martin viola katie palmer cello michael marchinetti bass noah smithdrelich piano sam kapala percussion  for building locations on the williams campus please consult the map outside the driveway entrance to the security office located in hopkins hall on main street rte  next to the thompson memorial chapel or call the office of public affairs   the map can also be found on the web at wwwwilliamseduhomecampusmap end williams college center for creative community development awarded  grant the zeiss planetarium sky section menu office of communications menu office of communications more resourcesmedia relationscalendar guidelinesdaily messages guidelinesstyle guidefast facts about williamsvisitor informationevent calendar thu  aug object not found a reading  pm at williams college museum of art wed  aug summer seminar  pm at williams college museum of art thu  aug the osmothèque  pm at williams college museum of art thu  aug seed library  pm at williams college museum of art subscribe » williams calendar »